討論區，只取少量內容，放link鼓勵點擊（尢其文宣大台該帶頭做）。<br />\n<br />\n再重覆，目標為上，才可以拯救連登垂死的熱門。<br />\n<br />\n比方說，<br />\n1. 如果兩日後有遊行，專注推行動Post；<br />\n2. 同一議題，集中處理，不要分散；<br />\n3. 有人留言「拉」，網友不需再留言；<br />\n4. 戒除政治J女性癖，不要再討論區議員身材；<br />\n5. 未能Fact Check的事情，忍痛讓佢沉。<br />\n6. 減少用極端字眼，例如「就嚟輸」；<br />\n7. 至為重要：不 要 再 推 假 標 題<br />\n<br />\n每個手足都有責任打好呢場資訊戰，改變習慣，重奪輿論主導權，大家一定做得到。<br />\n<br />\nYoutube戰線：黃色資訊片一律Coment+Like+Share&amp;Subscribe（CLS)（share做唔到的話重要片先share)<br />\n<br />\n香港人，改變。<br />\n<br />\nP.S.如果覺得有意思，煩請分享，謝謝你。<br />\n-------------------------------------------<br />\nIG：Terry_yeung_blog<br />\nIG連結：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2IMS6HI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2IMS6HI&d=1mfmSgVVN%2FWy7xf%2FaESqF5Khd8YmQljH21R%2F5cbT5WU%3D&h=8f3c52a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2IMS6HI</a>"},{"pid":"0a02b2ad662ca28c786c1ebd7ec84677047e34d9","tid":1889853,"uid":50386,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T00:58:42.000Z","msg":"俄佬都唔信支那啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9caee9b41b829795c10b95ebc882adf5fdb74d4","tid":1889853,"uid":76867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T00:59:32.000Z","msg":"最好作到呃埋自己啦<br />\n到時驚喜一浪接一浪"},{"pid":"85140aaf5505908f13011bbbbe7a3e6ba425627c","tid":1889853,"uid":78047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T01:01:56.000Z","msg":"又做假<br />\n睇下幾時冚唔住畀人踢爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfe042eefcf140dff03679d1e32410509877518f","tid":1889853,"uid":231583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T01:02:07.000Z","msg":"得啦得啦快d復工啦"},{"pid":"3f74882c159dd85ebfda0afe866990c47dfb503f","tid":1889853,"uid":276465,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T01:02:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/